title: Hevay Metal presents Moebius (1981) [CBR]
description:
Hevay Metal presents Moebius (1981) [CBR]

From back cover:
 "All new! Never before seen in the U.S.
 - A 44-page collaboration with El Topo's Jodorowsky! [the first volume of the Incal]
 - A gallery section displaying Moebius's illustrations of everything from movie posters to Gerald Ford (?) to French sf book ads to Western chivalry to soft porn."

I might add that apart from the already uploaded Incal story, this volume contains quite a few short story pearls.

Enjoy!
